trans-unit.source: Implements a set of predefined colors.
trans-unit.target: 實作一組預先定義的色彩。

trans-unit.source: The Windows Presentation Foundation color names match the .NET Framework, Windows Forms, and [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)] color names.
trans-unit.target: Windows Presentation Foundation 色彩名稱符合.NET Framework 中，Windows Form 和[!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)]色彩名稱。

trans-unit.source: This representation is based on UNIX X11 named color values.
trans-unit.target: 此表示法以 UNIX 為基礎 X11 名為色彩值。

trans-unit.source: The following image shows each predefined color, its name, and its hexadecimal value.
trans-unit.target: 下圖顯示每個預先定義的色彩，其名稱和十六進位值。

trans-unit.source: ![Predefined colors](~/add/media/art-color-table.png "Predefined colors")
trans-unit.target: ![預先定義的色彩](~/add/media/art-color-table.png "預先定義的色彩")

trans-unit.source: Color Table including a color swatch, the color name, and the hexadecimal value
trans-unit.target: 色彩表包括色樣、 色彩的名稱和十六進位值

trans-unit.source: See the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Brush> class for a variety of other more complex ways you can color an area, including gradients (<xref:System.Windows.Media.LinearGradientBrush>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.RadialGradientBrush>) or images (<xref:System.Windows.Media.ImageBrush>).
trans-unit.target: 請參閱<xref:System.Windows.Media.Brush>各種其他更複雜的方式，您可以色彩區域中，包括漸層的類別 (<xref:System.Windows.Media.LinearGradientBrush>， <xref:System.Windows.Media.RadialGradientBrush>) 或映像 (<xref:System.Windows.Media.ImageBrush>)。

trans-unit.source: Gets the system-defined color that has an [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_argb](~/includes/tlasharptla-argb-md.md)] value of <c>#FFFFFFFF</c>.
trans-unit.target: 取得系統定義的色彩，其 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_argb](~/includes/tlasharptla-argb-md.md)] 值為 <c>#FFFFFFFF</c>。

trans-unit.source: Represents colors in terms of alpha, red, green, and blue channels.
trans-unit.target: 表示 Alpha、紅色、綠色及藍色色頻方面的色彩。

trans-unit.source: For more information about color properties, see <xref:System.Windows.Media.Colors>.
trans-unit.target: 如需有關色彩屬性的詳細資訊，請參閱<xref:System.Windows.Media.Colors>。
